Key Match Events: Corey Seager hit a two-run home run in the third inning
Miscellaneous Highlights: Arizona's only run came in the eighth inning with an RBI single from Geraldo Perdomo
Others: Christian Walker got cut down at the plate in the second inning by Adolis Garcia
Diamondbacks second baseman Ketel Marte stretched his record postseason hitting streak to 19 games
Veteran starting pitcher Max Scherzer threw three innings before departing with back tightness
Garcia left the game late on after appearing to injure his side
